Package: portopt
Type: Package
Title: Basic Portfolio Optimization Tools
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Don Boyd
Maintainer: Don Boyd <donboyd5@gmail.com>
Description: Allows minimum-variance portfolio optimization with simple linear constraints on asset allocations.
    Can construct efficient frontier for a portfolio.
